<div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 20px;">Reset Your Password</h1>
  
  <p>Hello <%= @user.name %>,</p>
  
  <p>Someone has requested a password reset for your account. If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
  
  <p>To reset your password, click the link below:</p>
  
  <p style="margin: 30px 0;">
    <%= link_to "Reset Password", @reset_url, 
        style: "display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #2563eb; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px;" %>
  </p>
  
  <p>This link will expire in 2 hours.</p>
  
  <p>If you're having trouble clicking the button above, copy and paste the URL below into your web browser:</p>
  
  <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #4b5563;"><%= @reset_url %></p>
  
  <p style="margin-top: 40px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
    If you didn't request this password reset, you can safely ignore this email.
  </p>
</div> 